==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Utro-
<hw>U"tro-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A combining form used in anatomy to
indicate <xex>connection with</xex>, or <xex>relation to</xex>, <xex>the
uterus</xex>; as in <xex>utro</xex>-ovarian.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Utter</ent>⟦br⟧
